{"title_page": "Szombierki Coal Mine", "text_new": "{{Coord|50|20|18|N|18|54|39|E|display=title}} \n[[File:Szyb krystyna w Bytomiu ewa zieli\u0144ska.JPG|thumbnail|Krystyna winding tower at night]]\n'''Szombierki Coal Mine''' is a former [[coal mine]] in [[Szombierki]], [[Bytom]], [[Poland]]. It was created in 1870 from several smaller coal fields. From mid-1990s it begun to be retired.\n\nIn 2004 its [[winding tower]] \"Krystyna\" (formerly Kaiser Wilhelm) was added to the [[Polish register of monuments]].<ref>\u015al\u0105ski Wojew\u00f3dzki Konserwator Zabytk\u00f3w: [http://www.wkz.katowice.pl/documents/rejestr_zabytkow/gmina_bytom.doc Rejestr zabytk\u00f3w w Bytomiu]</ref>\n\nDuring a 2009 vote the tower was voted as one of the \"Seven Architectural Wonders of the [[Silesian Voivodeship]].\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://slaskie.pl/strona_n.php?jezyk=pl&grupa=10&art=3515&id_menu |title=Znamy 7 cud\u00f3w architektury wojew\u00f3dztwa \u015bl\u0105skiego |publisher=Slaskie.pl |date=2009-10-09 |accessdate=2014-03-07}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Poland-struct-stub}}\n\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Bytom]]\n[[Category:Szombierki]]\n[[Category:Coal mines in Silesian Voivodeship]]\n[[Category:1870 establishments in Prussia]]\n[[Category:Tourist attractions in Silesian Voivodeship]]\n", "text_old": "{{Coord|50|20|18|N|18|54|39|E|display=title}} \n[[File:Szyb krystyna w Bytomiu ewa zieli\u0144ska.JPG|thumbnail|Krystyna winding tower at night]]\n'''Szombierki Coal Mine''' is a former [[coal mine]] in [[Szombierki]], [[Bytom]], [[Poland]]. It was created in 1870 from several smaller coal fields. From mid-1990s it begun to be retired.\n\nIn 2004 its [[winding tower]] \"Krystyna\" (formerly Kaiser Wilhelm) was added to the [[Polish register of monuments]].<ref>\u015al\u0105ski Wojew\u00f3dzki Konserwator Zabytk\u00f3w: [http://www.wkz.katowice.pl/documents/rejestr_zabytkow/gmina_bytom.doc Rejestr zabytk\u00f3w w Bytomiu]</ref>\n\nDuring a 2009 vote the tower was voted as one of the \"Seven Architectural Wonders of the [[Silesian Voivodeship]].\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://slaskie.pl/strona_n.php?jezyk=pl&grupa=10&art=3515&id_menu |title=Znamy 7 cud\u00f3w architektury wojew\u00f3dztwa \u015bl\u0105skiego |publisher=Slaskie.pl |date=2009-10-09 |accessdate=2014-03-07}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Poland-struct-stub}}\n\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Bytom]]\n[[Category:Coal mines in Silesian Voivodeship]]\n[[Category:1870 establishments in Prussia]]\n[[Category:Tourist attractions in Silesian Voivodeship]]\n", "name_user": "He\u0142mPolski", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Szombierki_Coal_Mine"}
